<plot>Where lies the difference between justice and revenge? A cold-hearted Judge finds out when a seemingly crazy young couple break into his house and take him captive. The mystery guests soon unleash a stiff sentence of their own, without parole, teaching the Judge the consequence of doing unto others as you would have done unto you. By the end, only one thing is certain - justice is simply a toss of the coin.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?280499</url></doc>
